          org.grails.plugin.vaadin.utils.DomainProxy

class DomainProxy
extends groovy.util.Proxy

For adding equals() and hashCode() methods to domain classes using a proxy technique that leaves the domain class unchanged.

Authors:
Francis McKenzie
